        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm text-center" style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.25rem; text-align: center;">
          If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@eventoasis.com" class="footer-link footer-link-indigo" style="text-decoration: none; color: #4f46e5;">support@eventoasis.com</a>
